videos.headline: Taylor bounces to the outside for Wisconsin TD
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor scores his 12th touchdown of the season to put Wisconsin on the board first.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor bounces to the outside for Wisconsin TD) 2019/10/05

videos.headline: Taylor outruns Kent State's defense for 19-yard TD
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor rushes 19 yards for his second touchdown of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor outruns Kent State's defense for 19-yard TD) 2019/10/05

videos.headline: Taylor runs in his 3rd TD of the first half
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor gives Wisconsin a 21-0 lead after finding the end zone for the third time.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor runs in his 3rd TD of the first half) 2019/10/05

videos.headline: Taylor scores 4th TD with 18-yard reception
videos.description: Badgers QB Jack Coan rolls out and throws a quick pass to Jonathan Taylor, who cruises into the end zone for his fourth touchdown on the day.

videos.headline: Taylor hits the jets for his 5th TD
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor explodes up the middle for a 48-yard touchdown, his fifth of the day.
